::h3 break=page Answer 60

::fig sz=13 to=1 ca="Correct Answer"

Black 1 is the last point of profit left.

::dia sz=13 mv=K7D9 ca="Wrong Answer"

Black 1 is on a neutral point. White 2 takes the last profitable point. Black has lost a point.


