::h3 break=page Answer 72

::fig sz=13 to=1 ca="Correct Answer"

Black should play 1, connecting his four stones in atari to the ones above.

::dia sz=13 mv=G7G6 ca="Wrong Answer"

If Black captures two stones with 1, White captures four stones with 2.


